er) I agree, but considering that bard items (and even those of not high quality)cost an arm and a leg I'd only be able to do a mediocre job of twinking him compared to a lot of other twinks you can find on my server I can't even compare. I do have an idea of what to get but I'd like to see what the opinion of skilled bards are.  Honestly if you guys dislike me that much just because I've fought my way to get to where I am today thats quite an illogical way of thinking.  I'm actually a really nice guy if you get to know me and I've been known to hand down items like froggy robe, sword of morning, and other 5k-20k items to NEWBIES and I'm not talking about a friend or some twink, I mean some naked newbie who's wearing cloth at level 20.  So listen guys if you're on the seventh hammer send me a tell and get to know me, but honestly I came to the message board to extend a hand in PEACE and try to gain some insight on the class.  take this message however you choose but remember I'm not trying to attack anyone.<br><br>you can catch me on my trader toon which will be on for a while his name is Lorgrim, so if you're on the seventh hammer send me a tell and get to know me before you go making harsh judgements about me.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
